{"query_id":"q_vcdb_0012cc25_9167_40d8_8fe3_3d0dfd8fb6bb","source_id":"src_vcdb_validated_query","query_text":"Sensitive information belonging to jobseekers has been put at risk on the government's new Universal Jobmatch website, it has been reported. The security flaw was uncovered during a Channel 4 News investigation. Hackers were said to have been able to register as an employer on the site which is accessed through the Gov.uk portal – another website that has just been launched by the government to deliver more public services online. The hackers were reported to have obtained information including passwords and passport and driving licence scans after posting a fake advert for a cleaner on Universal Jobmatch.","query_values":{"external_query_scope":"source_extracted_external_observed_situation"},"query_origin":"source_extracted_incident_summary","attack_refs":[],"stripped_recommendation_text":true,"contains_recommendation_text":false,"identifier_fields":{"incident_id":"0012CC25-9167-40D8-8FE3-3D0DFD8FB6BB","action_keys":"hacking"},"leakage_notes":null,"text_provenance":{"text_origin":"normalized_verbatim","source_hash":"a93fbc68b9e1371c21d62f58d6c5279c3b3e310cc7bfe76af0233be941701c63","source_locator":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vz-risk/VCDB/master/data/json/validated/0012CC25-9167-40D8-8FE3-3D0DFD8FB6BB.json#summary","source_field":"summary","normalization_steps":["whitespace_normalization"],"semantic_paraphrase_forbidden":true}}
{"query_id":"q_vcdb_00163384_b4d7_46d5_9e6f_543dfb00f598","source_id":"src_vcdb_validated_query","query_text":"Veteran A returned a hard copy written prescription order for Veteran B that he received along with his appointment letter. The prescription order contained Veteran B's name, address, date of birth and medication information. This is informational for Mis-Handling incidents and is the representative ticket. There were a total of 87 Mis-Handling incidents this reporting period. Because of repetition, the other 86 are not included in this report, but are included in the \"Mis-Handling Incidents\" count at the end of this report. In all incidents, Veterans will receive a notification letter and/or credit monitoring will be offered if appropriate.","query_values":{"external_query_scope":"source_extracted_external_observed_situation"},"query_origin":"source_extracted_incident_summary","attack_refs":[],"stripped_recommendation_text":true,"contains_recommendation_text":false,"identifier_fields":{"incident_id":"00163384-B4D7-46D5-9E6F-543DFB00F598","action_keys":"error"},"leakage_notes":null,"text_provenance":{"text_origin":"normalized_verbatim","source_hash":"32614a9354655c541d3e442745351aad262ee956fcfcea4dde7d96c60426051b","source_locator":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vz-risk/VCDB/master/data/json/validated/00163384-B4D7-46D5-9E6F-543DFB00F598.json#summary","source_field":"summary","normalization_steps":["whitespace_normalization"],"semantic_paraphrase_forbidden":true}}
